data.description: The Westin, Built by Knight Homes, is a fabulous plan.  Some of the amazing features are Approx. 2715 Square foot, Coffered ceiling in the Dining room, Covered front porch, Classic trim series featuring crown molding, chair rail, and shadow boxes, Faux wood blinds on the front, Granite counter tops and tile back splash in the kitchen, Stainless steel appliances (Microwave, dishwasher, and range), screens on windows plus so much more.  The Knight Difference = Certified Professional Home Builder-honorable designation and recognized by Greater Atlanta Home Builder Association as Builder of the Year.
